    ${
      $d U r $.
      lpiss.u $e |- U = ( LIdeal ` R ) $.
      $( Principal ideal rings are where all ideals are principal.
         (Contributed by Stefan O'Rear, 3-Jan-2015.) $)
      islpir $p |- ( R e. LPIR <-> ( R e. Ring /\ U = P ) ) $=
